<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>PROPELLER SHAFT - INSTALL - Half Round End Yokes</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>Half Round End Yokes</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place jack stands under propeller shaft to support it during installation.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Rotate the transmission or axle end yoke so that the cross holes are in a horizontal
                position.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Holding propeller shaft tightly, position the bearing caps into the end yoke shoulders (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0600131">Figure 31</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f0600131" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g0600131" filename="../figg06/g0600131.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 31. Position Bearing Caps into End Yoke Shoulders</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Make sure bearing caps are seated correctly (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0600132">Figure 32</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f0600132" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g0600132" filename="../figg06/g0600132.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="392px" resolution="72"/>
                <caption>Figure 32. Make Sure Bearing Caps are Seated Correctly</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the straps over the bearing caps. Install the four bolts securing the bearing straps
                to the transmission, propeller, or axle end yoke.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten the bolts. Refer to the
                <hotlnk document="s06001_32.xml" xrefid="torquechart">TORQUE CHART
                    <xref refid="torquechart"/>
                </hotlnk>
                for torque specifications.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
